title: Cowboys Fans Gang Up To Beat Down A Packers Fans At Cowboys Stadium After Game
text:
Dallas Cowboys aren’t taking their loss too well. 
After today’s heartbreaking playoff loss the Packers, several Cowboys fans were filmed beating down on a poor Packers fan as he was leaving the stadium. 
Worldsta !! pic.twitter.com/FizlYrYUiO 
— Alex (@alexxvz_2897) January 16, 2017 

Stay classy, Dallas.
